2
00:00:00.370 --> 00:00:03.570
Iza te wo nobashite
Extend your hand, no need to fear

3
00:00:03.780 --> 00:00:06.740
Kaze wo kirisaite
Cut through the wind, and persevere

4
00:00:07.070 --> 00:00:11.410
Onore no chizu wo egaite yuke
Chart your own course, the time to push forward is here

5
00:00:16.390 --> 00:00:19.710
Migi mo hidari mo guchagucha ni
In a time like a storm, hear the tidal waves roar,

6
00:00:19.710 --> 00:00:22.750
Areta umi no youna jidai
we keep trudging along but we're still wanting more

7
00:00:22.960 --> 00:00:26.260
Kizukiageta kachikan sae mo
But in spite of it all, the foundation we built

8
00:00:26.260 --> 00:00:28.880
Kuzuresarou to shita
for ourselves was about to fall

9
00:00:29.470 --> 00:00:32.760
Rashinban no sashita saki ga
Where the compass points - Is it right? Is it wrong?

10
00:00:32.760 --> 00:00:35.470
Tadashii no ka douka nante
Who to ask? As if there's anyone listening

11
00:00:35.830 --> 00:00:38.810
Douse dare ni mo wakaranainda
I guess you'll never be one hundred percent sure

12
00:00:39.310 --> 00:00:42.270
Fukaku iki wo suikonde
But if you shut your eyes to the chaos,

13
00:00:42.560 --> 00:00:45.400
Hitomi tojireba
and you'd only take a breath

14
00:00:45.820 --> 00:00:48.700
Ukabiagaru no wa
When you open up your eyes

15
00:00:49.070 --> 00:00:52.410
Tamashii no shimesu michi
you will find where you were meant to be

16
00:00:52.780 --> 00:00:55.830
Iza te wo nobashite
Extend your hand, no need to fear

17
00:00:55.990 --> 00:00:59.040
Kaze wo kirisaite
Cut through the wind, and persevere

18
00:00:59.310 --> 00:01:03.920
Kurayami wo kettobashite
Kick out the dark until the sky clears

19
00:01:05.210 --> 00:01:08.090
Ima boku wa boku no tame ni
Even as we act in our own best interests,

20
00:01:08.260 --> 00:01:11.930
Kimi wa kimi no tame ni sou darou
doing what we each believe is for our own

21
00:01:12.390 --> 00:01:16.720
Onore no chizu wo egaite yuke
Chart your own course, the time to push forward is here

22
00:01:30.070 --> 00:01:32.910
Battle of Monsters on Onigashima

23
00:01:32.910 --> 00:01:37.290
You're still spouting that
nonsense, you wretched brat?!

24
00:01:37.290 --> 00:01:39.660
King of the Pirates?!

25
00:01:46.170 --> 00:01:49.050
His attack actually hurt me?

26
00:01:50.050 --> 00:01:54.470
So that's the haki that
the old man from Wano taught him...

27
00:01:54.470 --> 00:01:56.720
What the hell was that haki?

28
00:01:56.720 --> 00:01:58.930
Punches can hurt Kaido?!

29
00:02:00.770 --> 00:02:03.100
We could actually pull this off!

30
00:02:03.100 --> 00:02:08.360
More importantly, there's something
I have to tell Straw Hat...

31
00:02:08.780 --> 00:02:10.990
Hey, punk!

32
00:02:12.070 --> 00:02:19.620
Do you have any idea what it takes
to be King of the Pirates?!

33
00:02:25.000 --> 00:02:30.460
What happened after I crushed him in Kuri?

34
00:02:33.340 --> 00:02:35.590
Only a few people...

35
00:02:36.720 --> 00:02:40.140
have ever gone toe to toe with me.

36
00:02:46.690 --> 00:02:53.360
You... Do you really think
you're on their level?

37
00:02:54.320 --> 00:02:57.490
Straw Hat!

38
00:03:09.590 --> 00:03:12.050
Thunder Bagua!

39
00:03:20.890 --> 00:03:21.890
Dammit!

40
00:03:21.890 --> 00:03:24.810
I saw his attack coming,
but it was still too fast!

41
00:03:24.810 --> 00:03:26.190
Well done!

42
00:03:26.190 --> 00:03:29.310
You didn't take it head-on this time!

43
00:03:29.310 --> 00:03:31.690
You suck at this, Kaido!

44
00:03:31.690 --> 00:03:34.190
Trash should be burned!

45
00:03:35.320 --> 00:03:37.070
Prometheus!

46
00:03:37.070 --> 00:03:38.410
Yes, Mama!

47
00:03:39.280 --> 00:03:42.120
Let's burn them to ashes!

48
00:03:44.080 --> 00:03:46.210
Heavenly Feuer!

49
00:03:47.580 --> 00:03:50.420
Foxfire Style: Flame-Rend!

50
00:03:56.010 --> 00:03:58.050
Prometheus!

51
00:03:59.720 --> 00:04:01.220
Kin'emon's technique!

52
00:04:01.220 --> 00:04:03.470
That was awesome, Zoro!

53
00:04:05.730 --> 00:04:06.980
I stole it!

54
00:04:06.980 --> 00:04:09.400
Ow, ow, ow, ow!

55
00:04:09.400 --> 00:04:10.860
That hurt.

56
00:04:12.320 --> 00:04:14.400
Don't lower your guard for a second, Luffy!

57
00:04:15.320 --> 00:04:17.610
These are two Emperors we're dealing with!

58
00:04:22.780 --> 00:04:23.910
Shambles!

59
00:04:34.750 --> 00:04:36.710
Hey, Straw Hat.

60
00:04:36.710 --> 00:04:37.760
Traffy!

61
00:04:37.760 --> 00:04:39.630
You saved me! Thanks!

62
00:04:40.300 --> 00:04:41.640
Listen!

63
00:04:42.260 --> 00:04:44.390
Let's get one thing straight!

64
00:04:44.390 --> 00:04:45.060
Huh?

65
00:04:45.060 --> 00:04:47.020
I...

66
00:04:47.020 --> 00:04:50.600
was already planning
on moving them downstairs!

67
00:04:51.560 --> 00:04:52.520
Huh?!

68
00:04:52.520 --> 00:04:55.150
But then you said...

69
00:04:55.150 --> 00:04:55.940
Traffy!

70
00:04:55.940 --> 00:04:58.360
Send all of them downstairs!

71
00:05:00.660 --> 00:05:02.320
It sounded like...

72
00:05:02.320 --> 00:05:05.080
I was following your order!

73
00:05:05.080 --> 00:05:06.370
Huh?!

74
00:05:06.370 --> 00:05:08.330
Who cares about that?!

75
00:05:09.790 --> 00:05:11.420
Trafalgar...

76
00:05:12.040 --> 00:05:15.630
I thought you'd finally become
Straw Hat's lackey...

77
00:05:15.630 --> 00:05:17.590
N-No way!

78
00:05:17.590 --> 00:05:22.010
Not that I care which of you losers
answers to the other...

79
00:05:22.010 --> 00:05:23.260
– Huh?!
– Huh?!

80
00:05:23.260 --> 00:05:25.640
You're one to talk, loser!

81
00:05:25.640 --> 00:05:27.640
Who are you calling "loser"?!

82
00:05:27.640 --> 00:05:30.180
Quit your yapping!

83
00:05:30.180 --> 00:05:31.390
– Huh?!
– Huh?!

84
00:05:32.810 --> 00:05:35.060
Incinerate them all, Prometheus!

85
00:05:35.060 --> 00:05:36.650
Yes, Mama!

86
00:05:36.650 --> 00:05:38.940
Heavenly Bon-Bons!

87
00:05:43.160 --> 00:05:45.030
Okay, here's the deal!

88
00:05:45.030 --> 00:05:46.080
– Huh?!
– Huh?!

89
00:05:46.080 --> 00:05:50.120
The first one to dodge her attack is a loser!

90
00:05:50.120 --> 00:05:51.870
No way, you idiot!

91
00:05:51.870 --> 00:05:55.590
You always wanna play some stupid game!

92
00:05:55.590 --> 00:05:59.710
That's why you chumps
will never be big shots!

93
00:05:59.710 --> 00:06:00.970
Fine then!

94
00:06:00.970 --> 00:06:03.090
I guess you guys are losers!

95
00:06:03.090 --> 00:06:04.340
– Huh?!
– Huh?!

96
00:06:04.340 --> 00:06:06.510
Suit yourselves!

97
00:06:06.510 --> 00:06:08.010
Whatever!

98
00:06:08.010 --> 00:06:10.680
Why don't you run, you chickenshits?!

99
00:06:10.680 --> 00:06:12.810
Just dodge, you wimps!

100
00:06:15.350 --> 00:06:16.770
Hey, watch out!

101
00:06:28.200 --> 00:06:30.240
What are you guys doing?!

102
00:06:33.160 --> 00:06:37.790
Now who's gonna become
the King of the Pirates?!

103
00:06:37.790 --> 00:06:39.710
Let's see...

104
00:06:39.710 --> 00:06:42.970
How am I gonna kill you?

105
00:06:43.670 --> 00:06:45.720
Linlin, stand aside!

106
00:06:45.720 --> 00:06:48.050
I wanna see how strong they are.

107
00:06:48.800 --> 00:06:50.060
Huh?

108
00:06:50.060 --> 00:06:52.350
What's the point in that?

109
00:06:53.940 --> 00:06:56.940
Stay out of my way, Kamazo the Reaper!

110
00:06:59.320 --> 00:07:02.990
Nice laugh you've got there. Very distinct.

111
00:07:05.780 --> 00:07:10.620
You'd be dead if I had
my Punishers on back then.

112
00:07:10.620 --> 00:07:12.410
Zorojuro...

113
00:07:12.410 --> 00:07:13.790
I doubt it.

114
00:07:40.820 --> 00:07:42.860
Beheading Claws!

115
00:07:43.400 --> 00:07:44.940
Three-Sword Style:

116
00:07:46.650 --> 00:07:49.240
Purgatory Oni Giri!

117
00:08:07.380 --> 00:08:08.470
Too shallow!

118
00:08:16.350 --> 00:08:17.980
I'm impressed!

119
00:08:18.480 --> 00:08:22.940
I've gotta unleash Enma's power a bit more!

120
00:08:23.270 --> 00:08:24.480
Kaido!

121
00:08:26.490 --> 00:08:29.110
We're finishing this all at once!

122
00:08:29.110 --> 00:08:31.660
Gear Fourth!

123
00:08:54.180 --> 00:08:55.850
Boundman!

124
00:09:57.580 --> 00:09:58.740
Hell yeah!

125
00:10:00.620 --> 00:10:02.580
Punk Rotten!

126
00:10:14.930 --> 00:10:16.300
Room!

127
00:10:18.430 --> 00:10:19.350
Takt!

128
00:11:06.020 --> 00:11:10.480
These guys are damn near monsters!

129
00:11:10.480 --> 00:11:11.570
Bring it!

130
00:11:11.570 --> 00:11:14.700
Let's see if any of you
have what it takes to become...

131
00:11:15.820 --> 00:11:17.280
the King of the Pirates!

132
00:11:23.450 --> 00:11:26.580
Gum-Gum...

133
00:11:33.510 --> 00:11:35.510
Kong Gun!

134
00:11:47.940 --> 00:11:49.940
Ow...

135
00:11:49.940 --> 00:11:51.230
That stings!

136
00:11:54.650 --> 00:11:57.320
I know you've got some thick skin!

137
00:11:57.320 --> 00:12:01.200
But I bet I can still crush you to death!

138
00:12:06.830 --> 00:12:08.460
You asked for it!

139
00:12:08.460 --> 00:12:11.290
I'll show you how strong I am!

140
00:12:11.290 --> 00:12:13.340
Punk Vise!

141
00:12:32.400 --> 00:12:36.690
Not bad... but you'll need
more mass than that.

142
00:12:42.700 --> 00:12:45.450
Allow me to add some, then.

143
00:12:45.450 --> 00:12:46.660
What the...?!

144
00:12:46.660 --> 00:12:47.710
Takt!

145
00:12:49.710 --> 00:12:50.460
Damn!

146
00:13:02.390 --> 00:13:03.890
You bastard!

147
00:13:03.890 --> 00:13:06.060
Were you trying to kill me too?!

148
00:13:11.560 --> 00:13:13.940
Oh, that hurts!

149
00:13:13.940 --> 00:13:16.280
You're killing me!

150
00:13:17.480 --> 00:13:19.950
Pain like this...

151
00:13:29.500 --> 00:13:31.710
really takes me back!

152
00:13:37.590 --> 00:13:39.210
Yum-yum!

153
00:13:39.210 --> 00:13:41.800
I'm fully charged!

154
00:13:48.970 --> 00:13:52.640
Nice try, you little shits...

155
00:13:52.640 --> 00:13:57.320
I expect nothing less from idiots
who dream of being King of the Pirates...

156
00:14:01.360 --> 00:14:02.530
But...

157
00:14:03.110 --> 00:14:06.080
playtime is over!

158
00:14:19.050 --> 00:14:21.260
What a shame...

159
00:14:21.260 --> 00:14:25.260
None of you will last long at this point...

160
00:14:35.770 --> 00:14:40.440
And once you all die, I'll take everything...!

161
00:14:40.440 --> 00:14:45.700
Including each and every one of
your crew who followed you here!

162
00:14:47.070 --> 00:14:49.790
There's no way I'll let that happen!

163
00:14:52.830 --> 00:14:54.710
And we won't stop there!

164
00:14:54.710 --> 00:14:56.540
We're taking your treasure too!

165
00:14:56.540 --> 00:14:58.790
The poneglyphs.

166
00:14:58.790 --> 00:15:01.800
I bet you guys brought some along, right?

167
00:15:01.800 --> 00:15:03.380
I can't wait!

168
00:15:05.300 --> 00:15:08.800
You won't feel that way
when I take your crew and treasure!

169
00:15:12.180 --> 00:15:16.230
Whoever wins this battle
will be one big step closer...

170
00:15:16.230 --> 00:15:18.400
to becoming King of the Pirates!

171
00:15:19.980 --> 00:15:22.110
I'm the one who'll become...

172
00:15:22.610 --> 00:15:25.150
the King of the Pirates!

173
00:15:50.510 --> 00:15:52.010
Demolition Gust!

174
00:15:52.100 --> 00:15:52.140
Demolition
Gust

175
00:15:52.140 --> 00:15:52.180
Demolition
Gust

176
00:15:52.180 --> 00:15:54.350
Demolition

177
00:15:52.180 --> 00:15:52.220
Gust

178
00:15:52.220 --> 00:15:54.350
Gust

179
00:16:13.330 --> 00:16:14.160
Kid!

180
00:16:16.460 --> 00:16:18.370
It was a heap of scrap anyway!

181
00:16:22.710 --> 00:16:24.880
Kaido!

182
00:16:30.220 --> 00:16:33.850
You childish Pirate-King wannabes!

183
00:16:33.850 --> 00:16:36.810
Entertain me!

184
00:16:42.650 --> 00:16:46.650
Wano is mine to rule!

185
00:16:51.370 --> 00:16:54.700
Would you carry...

186
00:16:56.080 --> 00:16:58.540
Wano upon your back?!

187
00:17:16.720 --> 00:17:20.520
Gum-Gum...

188
00:17:20.520 --> 00:17:22.020
Kong...

189
00:17:22.900 --> 00:17:25.650
Rifle!

190
00:17:37.580 --> 00:17:41.790
Wake up, Mr. Emperor!

191
00:17:54.390 --> 00:17:57.850
Slam Gibson!

192
00:18:10.440 --> 00:18:11.740
Room!

193
00:18:13.070 --> 00:18:14.410
Shambles!

194
00:18:20.700 --> 00:18:23.580
I've never seen an anatomical
diagram of a dragon...

195
00:18:29.840 --> 00:18:32.550
but I'm guessing your heart
is right about here!

196
00:18:34.180 --> 00:18:35.760
Gamma Knife!

197
00:18:43.270 --> 00:18:46.060
I'll destroy you from within!

198
00:18:50.110 --> 00:18:51.820
How annoying!

199
00:19:03.160 --> 00:19:06.670
So you've realized how tough my body is!

200
00:19:06.670 --> 00:19:10.840
Looks like there's more
to you idiots than guts alone!

201
00:19:12.710 --> 00:19:15.380
These hard scales have been
a huge pain in the ass!

202
00:19:16.760 --> 00:19:19.760
How about I just cut into the body?!

203
00:19:26.770 --> 00:19:28.480
Scyther...

204
00:19:30.190 --> 00:19:31.860
Sonic!

205
00:19:43.540 --> 00:19:45.210
That did some damage, didn't it?!

206
00:19:47.670 --> 00:19:49.130
Kaido!

207
00:19:49.130 --> 00:19:50.500
Indra!

208
00:19:54.630 --> 00:19:56.130
Killer!

209
00:20:01.260 --> 00:20:04.470
As long as you're under the open sky,

210
00:20:04.470 --> 00:20:07.600
you have nowhere to run!

211
00:20:08.520 --> 00:20:14.440
They're more entertaining than I expected!

212
00:20:14.740 --> 00:20:17.780
Rhino Schneider!

213
00:20:23.660 --> 00:20:26.580
Good one!

214
00:20:33.500 --> 00:20:34.710
Traffy!

215
00:20:35.130 --> 00:20:36.970
Get me up there!

216
00:20:38.680 --> 00:20:41.680
Now you're telling me what to do...

217
00:20:43.890 --> 00:20:47.480
I'm not your servant! I don't answer to you!

218
00:20:48.140 --> 00:20:49.980
Foxfire Style...

219
00:20:55.230 --> 00:20:58.700
Blast Breath!

220
00:21:04.740 --> 00:21:06.750
...Flame-Rend!

221
00:21:12.670 --> 00:21:13.880
Zoro!

222
00:21:15.710 --> 00:21:17.340
One more time!

223
00:21:18.630 --> 00:21:20.050
Traffy!

224
00:21:20.050 --> 00:21:21.130
Huh?!

225
00:21:21.130 --> 00:21:25.140
I told you to stop using me as a tool!

226
00:21:33.310 --> 00:21:34.520
What the...?!

227
00:21:36.020 --> 00:21:37.730
Look out, Kaido!

228
00:21:38.110 --> 00:21:41.360
That's no ordinary sword!

229
00:21:41.360 --> 00:21:43.370
One-Sword Style:

230
00:21:52.670 --> 00:21:55.420
Flying Dragon Blaze!

231
00:22:06.810 --> 00:22:09.520
Why do I feel...

232
00:22:09.520 --> 00:22:12.690
Oden's presence in his sword?!

233
00:22:12.690 --> 00:22:14.310
Dammit!

234
00:22:14.310 --> 00:22:15.480
I missed!

235
00:22:15.480 --> 00:22:18.360
You seem to have underestimated us.

236
00:22:18.360 --> 00:22:20.280
Indra!

237
00:22:26.740 --> 00:22:28.290
Zoro!

238
00:22:31.870 --> 00:22:34.500
You've got no place to run!

239
00:22:35.750 --> 00:22:40.630
God of Lightning Tenjin!

240
00:22:48.140 --> 00:22:49.260
Dammit!

241
00:22:49.260 --> 00:22:51.060
A natural disaster, huh?!

242
00:23:27.010 --> 00:23:28.390
Straw Hat!

243
00:23:28.390 --> 00:23:31.890
Why didn't the lightning hurt you?!

244
00:23:38.310 --> 00:23:41.570
Because I'm rubber!

245
00:23:45.070 --> 00:23:47.780
You're gonna pay for hurting
Zoro and the others!

246
00:23:50.490 --> 00:23:52.370
Blast Breath!

247
00:24:23.530 --> 00:24:26.900
My flames didn't work either?! Why?!

248
00:24:30.200 --> 00:24:32.330
Guts!

249
00:24:34.290 --> 00:24:36.870
Gum-Gum...

250
00:24:41.380 --> 00:24:43.130
Kong...

251
00:24:47.090 --> 00:24:51.010
Gatling!
